    <h2> Credits </h2>
    <p style="font-size:1.2em"> ProVsion would not be possible without the wonderful open source community and of course the team at <b>R, Rstudio and shiny </b>. Open source packages for building this shiny app include <b> shinydashboard, shinyJS, colourpicker </b> and <b>shinywidgets </b>. Data handling with <b> dplyr </b>, while plotting is done with <b> ggplot2</b>  or <b>pheatmap </b> both of which allow for the beautiful graphs. Finally a big thanks to <b> LIMMA </b> for their package in analyzing this type of data, be sure to check out their  <a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/nar/gkv007" target="_blank"> publication </a>. </p>
